com.hp.jipp.dsl

Class ippPacket

  • com.hp.jipp.dsl.ippPacket

  • public class ippPacket

    DSL for defining an IPP packet. By default, the packet's versionNumber is set to DEFAULT_VERSION_NUMBER and its requestId is set to DEFAULT_REQUEST_ID.
